  <p class="bmh">ABOUT THE AUTHOR </p>
  <p class="tx1">KARIN SLAUGHTER is the internationally bestselling author of<em> A Faint Cold Fear</em>, which was named an International Book-of-the-Month Club selection, and<em> Blindsighted</em>, which was a<em> New York Times</em> bestseller and a Book Sense Top Mystery Pick. She is the author of<em> Kisscut</em> and<em> Indelible</em>, both international bestsellers, and contributed to and edited<em> Like a Charm</em>. A native of Georgia, she is currently working on<em> Triptych</em>, a stand-alone crime novel that Delacorte will publish in 2006. </p>
  <p class="tx">Visit the author at <a href="http://www.karinslaughter.com">www.karinslaughter.com</a>. </p>
